Name: Name Change, Frank Carvill Place, Borough of Queens.
Title: A Local Law in relation to naming Frank Carvill Place, Borough of Queens.

History.Description: This Introduction was Introduced by Council
This Introduction was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Parks and Recreation
This Introduction was Hearing Held by Committee
This Introduction was Laid Over by Committee
This Introduction was Sine Die (Filed, End of Session)

Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:

Section 1. The following intersection name, in the Borough of Queens, is hereby designated as hereafter indicated.

New Name	Present Name	Limits	
Frank Carvill Place	none	the intersection of Woodside Avenue and 59th Street	

Â§  2. This local law shall take effect immediately upon its enactment into law.




THC - 12/8/04
